info.name: Remove Cookie Consent
info.description: This style will remove most of those "I accept that our website is using cookies" boxes.
info.additionalInfo: So this is applying to all #ids that are named with "Cookie", "Privacy" or "Consent". It may hide also things that shouldn't be hidden. Keep that in mind

style.css: div[id^="cookie"], div[id*="cookie"],div[id^="Cookie"], div[id*="Cookie"],div[id^="privacy"], div[id*="privacy"],div[id^="Privacy"], div[id*="Privacy"],div[id^="consent"], div[id*="consent"],div[id^="Consent"], div[id*="Consent"]{display:none !important}
